divs: Sighting Details I was driving to Boise Id. when I saw a low circular cloud.I pulled out my camera and took three pics.I take pics. of clouds often so to see a low cloud like that was something that I just had to get a pic. of.I didn't notice the objects until two weeks later.In my pics. there are six round disks and one triangle two stream lines that go underneath the disks.I have an idea but I'm not sure what they are.I was looking at the sky the whole time while I was takeing the pics.and I never saw them until I was looking at them later.I also have a crop circle in my back yard for about one and a half years.I have other pics. of more UFOs.Thats all I'll say for now,if your interested please get in touch with me and I don't think it would be a waste of your time. Thank You Mike from Idaho
Object Shape: Bullet, Missile, Disc, Egg, Oval, Sphere, Triangle, Unknown
Summary: I was driving to Boise Id. when I saw a low circuler cloud,I took three pics. and the 2nd one has several UFOs in it.
